                                          "link": "23",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
                                            "22": {
                                              "id": "22",
                                              "speaker": "Korrilla",
                                              "text": "Excellent! A scheme of lunatics, a conspiracy of fools. I can't wait to see how it ends - with extreme violence and a hint of grotesque farce, I suspect.",
