                                    "11": {
                                      "id": "11",
                                      "speaker": "Korrilla",
                                      "text": "Might want to steer clear of my sister Hope, though. She's mad as a march hare. If she'd just agreed to serve Raphael, he'd probably have released her a long time ago.<br>",
                                      "context": "",
